metadata.name: Love Vending
metadata.description:
OK - I am simply obsessed with vending machines. Elegant, simple, non-judgmental, diligent, purposeful and discreet, they are ubiquitous and can be found along busy sidewalks, outside cozy shopfronts and tucked inside dark lonely alleyways. 

I examine life and the transactional nature of our interactions in Love Vending.
